{"tid":220433,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 慢煮麻醬雞絲粉皮","createTime":"2017-04-28T03:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T02:01:28.000Z","uid":30742,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f6c495176ab901ba2af0704fa46a94f207e79c1","tid":220433,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JZ05s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJZ05s.jpg&h=dada9289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/T3NLXKRBRSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT3NLXKRBRSM&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4ebf9fbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/T3NLXKRBRSM</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我平時都有做既雞絲粉皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為有時間想試下用慢煮黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下會唔會有分別<br />\n我撕雞絲果時覺得係好juicy，好嫩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過因為做左雞絲，食落又唔算係好大分別<br />\n但我下次再整都要用番慢煮，方便同埋都真係幾好食！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慢煮麻醬雞絲粉皮 圖文食譜: <br />\n<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/04/blog-post_27.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F04%2Fblog-post_27.html&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=885ceb35\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/04/blog-post_27.html</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6ba87952\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e86f8325\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1ed03613\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"114264cb3504e847de2d3dc0bd258ede545c40b7","tid":220433,"uid":5522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"30b55d513b2723359e713f49b209c8bf2797e1ee","tid":220433,"uid":5522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:03:53.000Z","msg":"最快今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40ee45ce40762358675eec2cd66e0324c3b44e0","tid":220433,"uid":58005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:05:59.000Z","msg":"嫁俾我 ok?"},{"pid":"ef5a0e17e1153f801e0214b1f9ff2aef019c8c75","tid":220433,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最快今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早晨！"},{"pid":"f32aa607a8116c5cd5e38a1f0e6088ac4a498c0d","tid":220433,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嫁俾我 ok?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i