你都可以試吓加橙汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8724465cc0f4e52e80d751f6b9c9bf6b1975d4ce","tid":220433,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到老娘正評左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273de39dee78120a5d98daf2e2e61ee00b8265fa","tid":220433,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔食同類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粉皮定雞絲先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f4872d4a8d039ce7b0ee94603178d6f27b6a79","tid":220433,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整過一次粉皮浸勁耐！！</blockquote><br />\n你係咪買乾身果隻？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果隻好難食的～你點浸或者同熱水拖都係難食！<br />\n無論係買一片定一條條都係難食！<br />\n我試過幾次！真係怕怕"},{"pid":"551b9097e68a87cb6d624451f69753b7684af71f","tid":220433,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麻醬好似唔岩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該稀少少再淡色啲</blockquote><br />\n我想掛得好d～影相好睇d嘛～唔會滲晒落底就睇唔見～<br />\n我個份量係會再稀少少～咁會易撈d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae42287015cd6561ffb8e9bd5d5f873a9ef3d79e","tid":220433,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個對你黎講肯定係幼稚園程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dd47a